com.ziluck.factions.spatial

Class BlockColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ziluck.factions.spatial.BlockColumn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.Geometry, com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.HasGeometry, com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.Rectangle

    public class BlockColumn
extends Object
implements com.github.davidmoten.rtree.geometry.Rectangle
    A two-dimensional location within a World. Similar to a LazyLocation, it allows storage of a location without requiring the World to also be loaded. The major difference is that it only uses the x and z values of the location in the World.
    Author:
    Michael Ziluck
